21856367,"The Innovators: How a Group of  Hackers, Geniuses and Geeks Created the Digital Revolution",147670869X,9781476708690,,B00JGAS65Q,ATVPDKIKX0DER,US,https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1410191571l/21856367._SX98_.jpg,https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1410191571l/21856367._SY75_.jpg,2014,10,7,Simon and Schuster,eng,false,"The computer and the internet are among the most important innovations of our era, but few people know who created them. They were not conjured up in a garret or garage by solo inventors suitable to be singled out on magazine covers or put into a pantheon with Edison, Bell, and Morse. Instead, most of the innovations of the digital age were done collaboratively. There were a lot of fascinating people involved, some ingenious and a few even geniuses. This is the story of these pioneers, hackers, inventors, and entrepreneurs—who they were, how their minds worked, and what made them so creative. It’s also a narrative of how they collaborated and why their ability to work as teams made them even more creative.”","{""id"":{""_"":""41129225"",""type"":""integer""},""books_count"":{""_"":""6"",""type"":""integer""},""best_book_id"":{""_"":""21856367"",""type"":""integer""},""reviews_count"":{""_"":""99542"",""type"":""integer""},""ratings_sum"":{""_"":""123027"",""type"":""integer""},""ratings_count"":{""_"":""30203"",""type"":""integer""},""text_reviews_count"":{""_"":""2155"",""type"":""integer""},""original_publication_year"":{""_"":""2014"",""type"":""integer""},""original_publication_month"":{""_"":""10"",""type"":""integer""},""original_publication_day"":{""_"":""7"",""type"":""integer""},""original_title"":""The Innovators: How a Group of Inventors, Hackers, Geniuses and Geeks Created the Digital Revolution"",""original_language_id"":{""type"":""integer"",""nil"":""true""},""media_type"":""book"",""rating_dist"":""5:12125|4:11160|3:4790|2:1264|1:864|total:30203"",""desc_user_id"":{""_"":""2026178"",""type"":""integer""},""default_chaptering_book_id"":{""type"":""integer"",""nil"":""true""},""default_description_language_code"":{""nil"":""true""},""work_uri"":""kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.zH2fK_IGDQOeTJtWQzPiAQ""}",4.07,542,Hardcover,,26428,1841,https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/21856367-the-innovators,https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/21856367-the-innovators,"{""author"":{""id"":""7111"",""name"":""Walter Isaacson"",""role"":"""",""image_url"":{""_"":""
